{"type":null,"faqId":45076,"title":"连接上热点后网速慢怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1. 建议您检查是否同时有其它设备使用网络，如正在使用电视秘盒看电视、笔记本下载电影等，如有建议您合理分配网络资源。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 使用Speedtest软件测试WLAN速率。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3. 建议您在靠近路由器的位置使用，避免丢包重传导致速率下降。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4. 您尽量不用手接触到手机的上方，尤其是音量键附近，那个区域是WLAN天线的位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5. 请确认是否使用了金属材质保护套，金属材质保护套对手机天线有影响，会导致手机信号变差，建议您使用塑料或皮质保护套。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"577","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409493000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":23,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"热点,网速慢","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}